OL,10,CG1987FLate evening News and Sport (BBC
OL,11,FOne) with Jan Leeming and David Icke is
OL,12,Fabandoned after a few minutes, due to a
OL,13,Ffire alarm. A small fire had broken out
OL,14,Fat BBC Television Centre. The bulletin
OL,15,Fwas rescheduled and broadcast at
OL,16,F11.15pm, with a short explanation about
OL,17,Fthe fire at the end of the bulletin.
